      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.9/x86_64, CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/30c43ef8-c8f4-11e2-97fe-52540035b04c).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
