        "subject": "LU-3367 lfsck: remove objects from OST",
        "message": "LU-3367 lfsck: remove objects from OST\n\nIn lfsck test, remove_objects() should remove objects from OST,\njust like remove_files() removes files from MDT. And add a version\ncheck to skip lfsck test on the servers for interop testing of\n2.1.6 clients on {2.1.6-, 2.2.0+, 2.3.65-} servers.\n\nThis patch also includes part of the following patches:\n\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/5981\nLustre-commit: 890f223c5f8f92b086d757ff545f45ea165b7a91\n\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/6206\nLustre-commit: 3d1305b528f370b893a77078489a04806f78b555\n\nTest-Parameters: testlist=lfsck\nSigned-off-by: Emoly Liu <emoly.liu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I9593317a5bf523f14e60be758246b88c02dc9581\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
